data.description: Beautiful 1.5 story home in North Liberty! John Glenn schools. Lots of updates to this home. New kitchen in 2020 with cabinets, granite countertops, and a tiled back splash. New stainless appliances in 2021. New first floor flooring. Updated full bath in 2018 that has a barn style sliding door. Remodeled family room in basement with an egress window added(2023). 1 bedroom on 1st floor and 2 up(one is a walkthrough). New light fixtures-2020. New on demand tankless gas water heater 2023. All new pex plumbing-2023. New roof and gutters are being installed-Nov 2023. New washer and dryer-2023. Huge back yard with a new privacy vinyl fence-May 2023. Exterior doors and storm doors- April 2022. New sewer line in back to alley. Deck and above ground pool(new liner 2022). 1 car detached garage. Great package deal. Call today to schedule a private showing!
